firefox.notes: Previously, the type of sandbox was a DOMString instead of a DOMSettableTokenList. This has been fixed with Gecko 29.0 (Firefox 29 / Thunderbird 29 / SeaMonkey 2.26)) (bug 845067). Other browsers may still implement the property as DOMString since it was a late change in the specification.
